EXTENDING A RIDGE OF HIGH PRESSURE ACROSS ICELAND AND SCANDINAVIA. LOW PRESSURE
LIES NEAR SEA AREA SHANNON WITH CENTRAL PRESSURE AROUND 988 WITH A CYCLONIC
PATTERN DOMINATING WERN UK SEA AREAS. PRESSURE WILL REMAIN HIGH ACROSS SCANDINAVIA
